{"tid":2109143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【信政府唔驚！】莊太量：美國取消對香港特殊待遇不算大事","createTime":"2020-07-15T04:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T20:32:40.000Z","uid":2054,"like":119,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"edbe1762095a21b7d827b685c7cd763bf94f2564","tid":2109143,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200715/NHTCYWM5D5FSTVZV56I7NUV5R4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200715%2FNHTCYWM5D5FSTVZV56I7NUV5R4%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu2t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=7f994892\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200715%2FNHTCYWM5D5FSTVZV56I7NUV5R4%2F&h=26cf1553\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200715/NHTCYWM5D5FSTVZV56I7NUV5R4/</a><br />\n<br />\n中大經濟學系副教授莊太量指，目前香港特別待遇地位主要是出入口關稅寬免，特別是高科技產品，取消特殊待遇對香港影響不大，因為香港對高科技產品使用量不大，不過措施或會影響中美出入口，減少香港轉口量。他補充，美國曾提及將懲罰個人或機構，但目前仍未有名單，暫時仍然是未知之數。他認為，美國與香港經濟關係細，香港經濟表現主要與內地掛鈎，包括旅客消費等，對於美國制裁會否令外商撤出香港，他分析指，香港資金一直進進出出，「香港從未試過啲錢永遠流走」，不算是一件大事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ACwLJ_NduOg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FACwLJ_NduOg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=53f70305&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"434d91afcb67d962e6a97826f495d24e0dc18e16","tid":2109143,"uid":267494,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"轉口走私<br />\n同埋中美前線科研交流基地既功能無左又唔講<br />\n呢篇野針對傻鳩藍絲聽眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a5a9da122dbdd4e0753e6182a85551d2d620e0","tid":2109143,"uid":218652,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"以前&quot;香港從未試過啲錢永遠流走&quot;，唔代表以後唔會"},{"pid":"5e6d299b13e39565af470f4cdbfb55946c0de9b0","tid":2109143,"uid":51271,"like":30,"dislike":1,"sco